raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.2.5" %}
{% set build_number = 1 %}
{% set min_rust = "rust >=1.54" %}

package:
  name: oxigraph
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/oxigraph/oxigraph/archive/refs/tags/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f9855472dcf746f97d80cba36ae95abdfa0b0429932b527f7288371c858bc6a8

build:
  number: {{ build_number }}

outputs:
  - name: oxigraph-server
    build:
      number: {{ build_number }}
      script:
        - bash {{ RECIPE_DIR }}/build-oxigraph.sh  # [unix]
        - call {{ RECIPE_DIR }}\bld-oxigraph-server.bat  # [win]
    requirements:
      build:
        - {{ compiler('c') }}                    # [unix]
        - {{ compiler('cxx') }}                  # [unix]
        - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}              # [win]
        - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}            # [win]
        - {{ min_rust }}
      host:
        - clangdev                               # [not osx]
        - openssl
    test:
      commands:
        - oxigraph_server --version
        - oxigraph_server --help

  - name: oxigraph-wikibase
    build:
      number: {{ build_number }}
      script:
        - bash {{ RECIPE_DIR }}/build-oxigraph.sh  # [unix]
        - call {{ RECIPE_DIR }}\bld-oxigraph-wikibase.bat  # [win]
    requirements:
      build:
        - {{ compiler('c') }}                    # [unix]
        - {{ compiler('cxx') }}                  # [unix]
        - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}              # [win]
        - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}            # [win]
        - {{ min_rust }}
      host:
        - clangdev                               # [not osx]
        - openssl
    test:
      commands:
        - oxigraph_wikibase --version
        - oxigraph_wikibase --help

  - name: pyoxigraph
    build:
      number: {{ build_number }}
      script:
        - bash {{ RECIPE_DIR }}/build-licenses.sh  # [unix and py==39]
        - call {{ RECIPE_DIR }}\bld-licenses.bat  # [win and py==39]
        - bash {{ RECIPE_DIR }}/build-oxigraph.sh  # [unix]
        - call {{ RECIPE_DIR }}\bld-pyoxigraph.bat  # [win]
    requirements:
      build:
        - {{ compiler('c') }}                    # [unix]
        - {{ compiler('cxx') }}                  # [unix]
        - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}              # [win]
        - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}            # [win]
        - {{ min_rust }}
        - maturin >=0.11,<0.12
      host:
        - clangdev                               # [not osx]
        - openssl
        - python
        - pip
      run:
        - python
    test:
      files:
        - test_licenses.py
      source_files:
        - python/tests
        - pyoxigraph-{{ version }}-cargo-dependencies.json  # [py==39]
      imports:
        - pyoxigraph
      commands:
        - pip check
        - python test_licenses.py --ignore oxigraph,oxigraph_js,oxigraph_server,oxigraph_testsuite,oxigraph_wikibase,pyoxigraph  # [py==39]
        - cd python/tests
        - pytest -vv --cov pyoxigraph --cov-report term-missing:skip-covered --cov-fail-under 100
      requires:
        - pip
        - pytest-cov
        - ruamel_yaml
        # fails pip check: https://github.com/conda-forge/importlib_metadata-feedstock/issues/88
        - importlib-metadata !=4.7.1
